'''苯丁酸'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>12</sub>O<sub>2</sub>。

==合成==
苯丁酸可由3-丙烯酸和硼酸的偶联反应制得。<ref>Li, Zi-Qi; Fu, Yue; Deng, Ruohan; Tran, Van T.; Gao, Yang; Liu, Peng; Engle, Keary M. Ligand-​controlled regiodivergence in nickel-​catalyzed hydroarylation and hydroalkenylation of alkenyl carboxylic acids. ''ChemRxiv'', 2020. pp 1-8. ISSN: 2573-2293.</ref>γ-苯基丁内酯<!-- CAS 1008-76-0 -->的加氢开环反应也能得到苯丁酸。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Organic Letters|volume=21|issue=17|language=en|issn=1523-7060|date=2019-09-06|pages=7099–7103|doi=10.1021/acs.orglett.9b02673|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.orglett.9b02673|title=Strategic Approach to the Metamorphosis of γ-Lactones to NH γ-Lactams via Reductive Cleavage and C–H Amidation|accessdate=2020-11-18|author=Hoi-Yun Jung, Sukbok Chang, Sungwoo Hong}}</ref>

其它合成方法还包括苯丁酸衍生物的水解<ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=2006|issue=23|language=en|date=2006-12|pages=5238–5242|doi=10.1002/ejoc.200600699|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/ejoc.200600699|title=Exploring the Synthetic Applicability of a Cyanobacterium Nitrilase as Catalyst for Nitrile Hydrolysis|accessdate=2020-11-18|author=Chandrani Mukherjee, Dunming Zhu, Edward R. Biehl, Ling Hua}}</ref><!--腈--><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Tetrahedron Letters|volume=61|issue=44|language=en|date=2020-10|pages=152467|doi=10.1016/j.tetlet.2020.152467|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040403920309485|title=Activated charcoal as an effective additive for alkaline and acidic hydrolysis of esters in water|accessdate=2020-11-18|author=Kiyoshi Tanemura, Taoufik Rohand}}</ref><!--酯-->、苯丁醇的氧化<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry Letters|volume=36|issue=2|language=en|issn=0366-7022|date=2007-02|pages=212–213|doi=10.1246/cl.2007.212|url=http://www.journal.csj.jp/doi/10.1246/cl.2007.212|title=Synthetic Application of PVP-stabilized Au Nanocluster Catalyst to Aerobic Oxidation of Alcohols in Aqueous Solution under Ambient Conditions|accessdate=2020-11-18|author=Hironori Tsunoyama, Tatsuya Tsukuda, Hidehiro Sakurai|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701001048/https://www.journal.csj.jp/doi/10.1246/cl.2007.212|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。

